{"parents": [{"link": "../../../", "title": "CRM"}], "prev": {"link": "../details/", "title": "Details"}, "next": {"link": "../programs/", "title": "Programs"}, "title": "Lists", "meta": null, "body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"lists\">\n<h1>Lists<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#lists\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<div class=\"line-block\">\n<div class=\"line\"><strong>Lists</strong> displays the name of the contact groups of a program.</div>\n</div>\n<ol class=\"arabic\">\n<li><p>Click <i class=\"fa fa-bars\"></i> in the ribbon</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>CRM</strong></p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Programs</strong></p></li>\n<li><p>Click a program</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Lists</strong></p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Add List</strong></p></li>\n<li><p>Enter a list name</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>Save</strong></p></li>\n<li><p>Click <i class=\"fa fa-ellipsis-v\"></i> to edit the list, create a workflow, or delete the list</p></li>\n<li><p>Click <strong>X Contacts</strong> to view the contacts that belong to the list</p>\n<ul class=\"simple\">\n<li><p>To add a contact to a list, refer to <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/crm/guides/contacts/add_contact.html\">Adding a Contact to a List or a Program</a></p></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><p>Click the tab entitled <strong>Automations</strong> to view <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/workflows.html\">workflows</a></p>\n<p><em>Click **Create Workflow*</em> to create a <a class=\"reference external\" href=\"/users/automation/guides/workflows/create_a_workflow.html\">new workflow</a></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>To view another template, click <i class=\"fa fa-chevron-left\"></i> and choose the desired template</p></li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n", "metatags": "", "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["users/crm/guides/programs/programs", "Programs", "N", "next"], ["users/crm/guides/programs/details", "Details", "P", "previous"]], "sour